item.title: CVE-2021-20720|2024-08-03T17:53:21.250Z -- kujirahand -- konawiki2
item.description: SQL injection vulnerability in the KonaWiki2 versions prior to 2.2.4 allows remote attackers to execute arbitrary SQL commands and to obtain/alter the information stored in the database via unspecified vectors.

item.title: CVE-2021-20721|2024-08-03T17:53:21.815Z -- kujirahand -- konawiki2
item.description: KonaWiki2 versions prior to 2.2.4 allows a remote attacker to upload arbitrary files via unspecified vectors. If the file contains PHP scripts, arbitrary code may be executed.
